Global Food Grater Market Insights
Food Grater Market size was valued at USD 2.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 3.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.0% from 2024 to 2030.

Food Grater Market Overview
The global food grater market is valued at USD 1.2 billion in 2024, with an expected annual growth rate of 5.2% during the forecast period. The increasing demand for convenience kitchen tools and rising popularity of home cooking, driven by more people cooking at home, are significant factors fueling the growth of the market. The food grater market benefits from continuous innovation in design, material, and functionality, with manufacturers offering diverse types of graters, including manual, electric, and multi-functional models. Furthermore, the trend of healthy eating, coupled with growing demand for food preparation tools, is expected to maintain a positive market outlook in the coming years.

